{"tid":1796941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳今日心情唔靚 唔去台灣了","createTime":"2019-12-25T04:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T06:22:20.000Z","uid":785,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db8883d50ac4c88ecffb1aa16745f430951a4804","tid":1796941,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191225/bkn-20191225014014527-1225_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191225%2Fbkn-20191225014014527-1225_00822_001.html&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=4b75e204\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191225/bkn-20191225014014527-1225_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣殺人案疑兇陳同佳在今年10月出獄，至今已超過兩個月，惟暫未有赴台灣自首的時間表。早前說服陳自首的香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴表示，直至今天（25日）為止，陳並無改變去台灣自首的意欲，一旦決定時間將會對外作出交代。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳10月刑滿出獄後，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>管浩鳴當時指，原本已購買出獄當日前往台灣的機票，但因台灣禁制二人入境，已取消機票，亦不清楚何時會前往當地，又指由於台方訊息混亂，經常每日轉換口風，令陳心情亦受到影響。</strong></span>其後港台兩地就陳自首一事不斷放話及針鋒相對，變成新一輪政治風波。<br />\n<br />\n佳哥好食好住，幾時會心情靚，肯去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa5eda240e4caeb7549213216cafae8566cce9a","tid":1796941,"uid":68620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"玩多四五十年先啦<br />\n去唔到台灣未去大灣區lo<br />\n個度大把人會幫佢"},{"pid":"dc385e9633e41af1592b1310163fb589059bf8f8","tid":1796941,"uid":181744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"台灣講多次話要過黎拎人就好睇"},{"pid":"17b8a0d05c2241c43d0e50f27a8e9a0119343fcf","tid":1796941,"uid":167330,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTOJ3o7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTOJ3o7.png&h=c1200892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165a6b4a